title: Don’t Let This One Pass You By! Will Go Fast 3 Bedroom!
posting_body: ['Our one, two, and three bedroom apartments at Cedar Ridge will give you the feel of luxury at an affordable price.', 'Conveniently located in Hudson, WI you will have numerous shopping, dining, and entertainment options right at your fingertips!', 'Call today for more information!', 'Community Amenities Include:', '- Large & Comfortable Living Room', '- In-Home Air-Conditioning System', '- Ample Off-Street Open Parking', '- Beautiful Grassland Views', '- Pet Friendly Community', '- High-Speed Internet & Cable Ready', '- Easy Access To Walking & Biking Paths', 'We are a pet friendly community!', 'Dogs & cats welcome!', '*Comfortable living does not have to be high dollar.', 'Cedar Ridge participates in an affordable housing program.', 'Household income & student status limitations apply: 1 Occupant: $49,320 | 2', 'Occupants: $56,340 | 3', 'Occupants: $63,360 | 4 Occupants: $70,380 | 5 Occupants: $76,020 | 6', 'Occupants: $81,660.', 'To maintain the integrity of the community; credit, rental & public record background checks are conducted on all applicants.', 'Office Hours:', 'Monday-Tuesday: 9:00AM-5:00PM', 'Wednesday: 11:00AM-7:00PM', 'Thursday-Friday: 9:00AM-5:00PM', 'Call today to learn more about our community:', 'show contact info', 'Cedar Ridge', '1401 Namekagon Avenue', 'Hudson, WI, 54016', '<URL>', '*Some Restrictions May Apply.', 'OA14DqAKO']
